\c 8
\s Dambudziko rechipiri: Matacha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Pinda kuna Farao, ugoti kwaari: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Rega vanhu vangu vaende, kuti vanondishumira\x + 8.20; 3.12,18.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino kana uchiramba ku\add va\add*rega vaende\x + 7.14; 9.2.\x*, tarira, ndicharova muganhu wako wose nematacha\x + Zvak. 16.13.\x*.
\v 3 Nerwizi rwuchafararika nematacha, uye achakwira ndokupinda mumba mako, nemumba mako mekurara\x + Map. 105.30. Gen.. 43.30.\x*, nepamusoro pemubhedha wako, nemumba mevaranda vako, nepamusoro perudzi rwako, nemuzvoto zvako, nemumidziyo yako yekukanyira \add zvekudya.\add*
\v 4 Zvino matacha achakwira pauri nepamusoro perudzi rwako nepamusoro pevaranda vako vose.
\p
\v 5 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Mozisi: Iti kuna Aroni: Tandavadza ruoko rwako\x + 7.19.\x* pamwe netsvimbo yako pamusoro pehova, pamusoro penzizi, nepamusoro pemadziva, ukwidze matacha pamusoro penyika yeEgipita.
\v 6 Aroni ndokutandavadza ruoko rwake pamusoro pemvura dzeEgipita; matacha ndokukwira, ndokufukidza nyika yeEgipita\x + Map. 78.45; 105.30.\x*.
\v 7 N'anga ndokuita saizvozvo neuroyi hwadzo\x + 7.11,22.\x*, ndokukwidza matacha pamusoro penyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Farao wakadana Mozisi naAroni, ndokuti: Nyengeterai kuna Jehovha\x + 8.9,28,29,30; 9.28; 10.17,18.\x* kuti abvise matacha kubva kwandiri nekubva kurudzi rwangu; zvino ndicharega rudzi rwuende kuti vabaire kuna Jehovha.
\v 9 Mozisi ndokuti kuna Farao: Kudzwai pamusoro pangu! Ndinokunyengetererai rinhi, uye varanda venyu uye rudzi rwenyu, kuparadza matacha kubva kwamuri, nekubva kudzimba dzenyu, asare murwizi chete?
\v 10 Iye ndokuti: Mangwana. Iye ndokuti: Seshoko renyu, kuti muzive kuti hakuna wakafanana naJehovha Mwari wedu\x + 9.14. 2 Sam. 7.22. 1 Makor. 17.20. Map. 86.8. Isa. 46.9. Jer. 10.6,7.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino matacha achabva kwamuri, nekudzimba dzenyu, nekuvaranda venyu, nekurudzi rwenyu; achasara murwizi chete.
\v 12 Mozisi naAroni ndokubuda kubva kuna Farao, Mozisi ndokudana kuna Jehovha maererano nenyaya yematacha aaiva aisira Farao.
\v 13 Jehovha ndokuita maererano neshoko raMozisi; matacha ndokufa kubuda mudzimba, kubuda mumisha, nekubuda muminda.
\v 14 Zvino vakaaunganidza mirwi nemirwi, nyika ndokunhuhwa.
\v 15 Asi Farao aona kuti zvambozorora\x + Esi. 4.14. Mup. 8.11.\x*, ndokuremesa moyo wake\x + 8.32; 7.14; 9.7,34; 10.1.\x*, uye haana kuvateerera, Jehovha sezvaaiva ataura.
\s Dambudziko rechitatu: Utunga
\p
\v 16 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Iti kuna Aroni: Tandavadza tsvimbo yako, ugorova guruva repasi, rigova utunga panyika yose yeEgipita.
\v 17 Zvino vakaita saizvozvo; nokuti Aroni wakatandavadza ruoko rwake\x + 7.19.\x* netsvimbo yake, ndokurova guruva repasi, utunga ndokuva\add po\add* pavanhu nepazvipfuwo\x + Map. 105.31.\x*; guruva rose repasi rikava utunga panyika yose yeEgipita.
\v 18 N'anga ndokuita saizvozvo neuroyi hwadzo\x + 7.11.\x* kubudisa utunga, asi hadzina kugona; naizvozvo utunga hwaiva pavanhu nepazvipfuwo.
\v 19 Zvino n'anga dzakati kuna Farao: Uyu munwe waMwari\x + Map. 8.3. Ruk. 11.20.\x*. Asi moyo waFarao wakava wakaoma\x + 7.13.\x*, zvino akasavateerera, Jehovha sezvaaiva ataura.
\s Dambudziko rechina: Nhunzi
\p
\v 20 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Muka mangwanani-ngwanani, ugozvimisa pamberi paFarao\x + 7.15; 9.13.\x*; tarira, anobudira kumvura, zvino uti kwaari: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Rega vanhu vangu vaende, kuti vandishumire\x + 8.1.\x*.
\v 21 Nokuti kana usingaregi vanhu vangu vaende, tarira, ndichatuma fararira \add renhunzi\add* pamusoro pako, nepamusoro pevaranda vako, nepamusoro perudzi rwako, nemudzimba dzako; nedzimba dzeVaEgipita dzichazara nemafararira \add enhunzi\add*, uyewo ivhu padziri.
\v 22 Uye ndichaparadzanisa muzuva iro nyika yeGosheni\x + 9.4; 11.7.\x* mugere rudzi rwangu mairi, kuti pasavapo nefararira \add renhunzi\add*; kuti uzive kuti ndini Jehovha pakati penyika\x + 8.10; 7.17.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino ndichaisa mutsauko pakati perudzi rwangu nerudzi rwako; mangwana kuchava nechiratidzo ichi.
\v 24 Zvino Jehovha wakaita saizvozvo; mafararira makuru \add enhunzi\add* ndokusvika\x + Map. 78.45; 105.31.\x* mumba maFarao, nemudzimba dzevaranda vake, nemunyika yose yeEgipita; nyika yakaodzwa nekuda kwemafararira \add enhunzi\add*.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Farao wakadana Mozisi naAroni, ndokuti: Endai, mubaire kuna Mwari wenyu munyika ino.
\v 26 Mozisi ndokuti: Hazvina kunaka kuita saizvozvo, nokuti tichabaira zvinonyangadza zveVaEgipita kuna Jehovha\x + Gen.. 43.32; 46.34.\x*, Mwari wedu. Tarirai, tikabaira zvinonyangadza zveVaEgipita pamberi pemeso avo, havangatitaki nemabwe here\x + 17.4.\x*?
\v 27 Tichaenda rwendo rwemazuva matatu murenje, tigobaira kuna Jehovha Mwari wedu, sezvaachataura kwatiri\x + 3.18,12.\x*.
\v 28 Farao ndokuti: Ini ndichakuregai muende, kuti mubaire kuna Jehovha Mwari wenyu murenje; koga musaenda kure-kure. Ndinyengetererei\x + 8.8.\x*.
\v 29 Mozisi ndokuti: Tarirai, ndinobuda kubva kwamuri, uye ndichanyengetera kuna Jehovha kuti mafararira \add enhunzi\add* abve kuna Farao, kubva kuvaranda vake nekubva kurudzi rwake mangwana; koga Farao ngaarege kuwedzera kunyengera pakurega kuregedza rudzi rwuende kunobaira kuna Jehovha\x + Gen.. 31.7. Vato. 16.10,15. Job. 13.9.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Mozisi ndokubuda kubva kuna Farao, ndokunyengetera kuna Jehovha.
\v 31 Jehovha ndokuita maererano neshoko raMozisi, ndokubvisa mafararira \add enhunzi\add* kubva kuna Farao, kubva kuvaranda vake, nekubva kurudzi rwake; hakuna kusara imwe.
\v 32 Asi Farao wakaremesa moyo wake\x + 8.15.\x* panguva iyiwo, uye haana kurega rudzi rwuende.